===Noun===
'''Christian name'''

#A [[first name]] formally given to a child at a Christian baptism.
#(''by extension'') Any forename.

====Usage note====
Many non-Christians find this term offensive when used to refer to a non-Christian. If you wish to avoid offence when referring to the name of a person who is not or might not be a Christian, or to the name of a non-specific person, use one of the synonyms below.

